er, J.R., (1955) The water balance. Publications in Climatology, p. 104. , Philadelphia: Drexel Institute of Technology; Tubiello, F.N., Donatelli, M., Rosenzweig, C., Stockle, C.O., Effects of climate change and elevated CO 2 on cropping systems: Model predictions at two Italian locations (2000) European Journal of Agronomy, 13, pp. 179-189; Zullo Júnior, J., Pinto, H.S., Assad, E.D., Impact assessment study of climate change on agricultural zoning (2006) Meteorological Applications, 1, pp. 69-80","Sentelhas, P. C.; USP/ESALQ, Depto. de Engenharia Rural, Av. Pádua Dias, 11, 13418-900 - Piracicaba, SP, Brazil; email: pcsentel@esalq.usp.br",,,,,,,,01039016,,,,"Portuguese","Sci. Agric.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-70350413420
